<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset=UTF-8">
  <tiltle>Street Bites</title>
  <meta name="viewpoint" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
  body { 
   font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
   margin: 0;
   backgroung: #111;
   color: white;
   }
   header { 
   background: #ff3c00;
   padding: 20px;
   text-align: center;
   }
   nav a { 
   color: white;
   margin: 0 15px;
   text-decoration: none;
   font-weight: bold;
   }
   .hero {
   text-align: center;
   padding: 50px 20px;
   background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550547660-d9450f859349') no-repeat center/cpver;
   }
   .hero h1 {
   font-size: 40px;
   color: white;
   }
   .menu {
   display: flex;
   flex-wrap: wrap;
   justify-content: center;
   padding: 20px;
   }
   .card {
   background: #222;
   margin: 15px;
   padding: 20px;
   width: 250px;
   border-radius: 10px;
   text-align: center;
   }
   .card h3 {
   color: #ff3c00;
   }
   .contact {
   background: black;
   padding: 30px;
   text-align: center;
   }
   .btn {
   background: #25D366;
   color: white;
   padding: 12px 20px;
   text-decoration: none;
   border-radius: 5px;
   display: inline-block;
   margin-top: 10-px;
   }
   </style>
   </head>
   <body>
   <header>
   <h1>Sreet Bite</h1>
   <p>Burgers Dagwoods Wings Chips Drinks</p>
   </header>
   <nav>
   <a href="#">Home</a>
   <a href="#">Menu</a>
   <a href="#">Contact</a>
   </nav>
   <section class="hero">
   <h1>Fresh. Hot. Delicious.</h1>
   <p>Your favourite fast food spot in eKasi</P>
   </section>
   <section class="menu">
   <div class="card">
   <h3>Burgers/Dagwoods</h3>
   <p>Juicy and tasty burgers and dagwoods made fresh.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="card">
   <h3>Chips</h3>
   <p>Hot and crispy fries.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="card">
   <h3>Wings</h3>
   <p>Spicy, BBQ and crispy wings.</P>
   </div>
   <div class="card">
   <h3>Drinks</h3>
   <p>Mocktails and refreshing cocktails.</p>
   </div>
   </section>
   <section class="contact">
   <h2>Order Now</h2>
   <p>Contact us on WhatsApp</p>
   <a class="btn" href=https://wa.me/0812624641">Order on WhatsApp</a>
   </section>
   </body>
   </html>
   
   
